Package com.symbian.commdb.data

Class Summary
Database This class contains all the CommDB tables.
EnumerationType This class defines a generic enumeration type composed of a number of Strings to be used for describing the various enumeration types of the CommDB table parameters
Table This class specifies a table in CommDB which can contain any number of table entries (TableEntry class), all based on a particular table template (TableTemplate class)
TableEntry This class represents a particular entry of a CommDB table and it contains all the values for the parameters of this entry.
TableTemplate This class describes a particular CommDB table and it contains all the parameters of the table.
Version This class implements the version of the CommDB Editor engine
 

Exception Summary
DatabaseException This is an exception thrown by a member method of the com.symbian.commdb.data.* class in case of an error during the processing of the database
